OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783680590
OL,3,CBusinesses back campaign to cut VAT
OL,4,Camid 'unsustainable' financial
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,FWelsh hospitality businesses are
OL,8,Furging the UK Government to slash VAT
OL,9,Fto help protect the sector as 'soaring
OL,10,Fcosts' make it 'increasingly harder'
OL,11,Fto survive.
OL,13,FIt comes as business owners across the
OL,14,Fcountry have backed the 'VAT's the
OL,15,FProblem' campaign, calling on the UK
OL,16,FGovernment to cut the hospitality VAT
OL,17,Frate from 20% to 10%.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783680590
OL,3,CBusinesses back campaign to cut VAT
OL,4,Camid 'unsustainable' financial
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,FFronted by celebrity chef Tom
OL,8,FKerridge, the campaign argues the UK's
OL,9,Fhospitality VAT rate is among the
OL,10,Fhighest in Europe and is placing
OL,11,Funsustainable pressure on pubs, cafes,
OL,12,Frestaurants and hotels.
OL,14,FAmong those supporting the campaign is
OL,15,FBridie Phillips, who owns Coco's Cafe
OL,16,Fin Aberdare. She told ITV Wales that
OL,17,Fdespite running two successful cafes,
OL,18,Fthe family business is struggling to
OL,19,Fkeep up with mounting costs.
OL,26,@sD@drrwD@erryD@crr
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783680590
OL,3,CBusinesses back campaign to cut VAT
OL,4,Camid 'unsustainable' financial
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,FShe said: "We're a great example of a
OL,8,Fbusy business that is doing really
OL,9,Fwell on the outside but at the end of
OL,10,Fthe month, the money just doesn't add
OL,11,Fup. Everything is going out, and even
OL,12,Fthough a lot is coming in as well, it
OL,13,Fjust doesn't add up anymore."
OL,15,FShe says businesses have been hit by
OL,16,Frising wages, energy bills, inflation,
OL,17,Fbusiness rates and National Insurance
OL,18,Fcosts, but believes a reduction in VAT
OL,19,Fwould provide much-needed relief.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783680590
OL,3,CBusinesses back campaign to cut VAT
OL,4,Camid 'unsustainable' financial
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,FShe continued: "It is our largest cost
OL,8,Fgoing out, it comes into the tens of
OL,9,Fthousands. Every quarter when that
OL,10,Fbill drops, it's a scary prospect and
OL,11,Fall of us are in the same boat."
OL,13,FDespite serving around 1,500 customers
OL,14,Feach week, she says trade is no longer
OL,15,Fstrong enough to absorb rising costs.
OL,17,FWorking around 70 hours a week each,
OL,18,Fthe family says there is often little
OL,19,Fleft at the end of the month, leaving
OL,20,Fthem questioning whether running the
OL,21,Fbusiness is worthwhile.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783680590
OL,3,CBusinesses back campaign to cut VAT
OL,4,Camid 'unsustainable' financial
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,FAfter deciding to open her cafe in
OL,8,FAberdare to help boost the town, she
OL,9,Fnow fears that without action, high
OL,10,Fstreets could become increasingly
OL,11,Fdesolate.
OL,13,FBridie is not alone, across the
OL,14,Fcountry, other businesses are sharing
OL,15,Fher concerns.
OL,17,FDavid Evans, CEO and co-founder of
OL,18,FDylan's Restaurants in North Wales,
OL,19,Fwould also support a cut to VAT.
OL,26,@oD@_rr
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783680590
OL,3,CBusinesses back campaign to cut VAT
OL,4,Camid 'unsustainable' financial
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,FHe said: "Unfortunately our
OL,8,Foperational costs are growing faster
OL,9,Fthan what our sales can keep up with.
OL,11,FHe added: "When we look around Europe,
OL,12,Fother government's have figured it
OL,13,Fout. You can't keep taxing hospitality
OL,14,Fbusinesses that pay no input VAT but
OL,15,Fpay all the output VAT. It's an
OL,16,Funsustainable equation."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783680590
OL,3,CBusinesses back campaign to cut VAT
OL,4,Camid 'unsustainable' financial
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,FDylan's, which opened its first
OL,8,Frestaurant in 2012, has since grown to
OL,9,Femploy around 200 members of staff,
OL,10,Fwhile sourcing produce from and
OL,11,Fsupporting local suppliers and
OL,12,Fbusinesses across Wales.
OL,14,FBut Mr Evans said the growing
OL,15,Ffinancial pressures facing hospitality
OL,16,Fbusinesses are becoming unsustainable
OL,17,Fand warned the consequences would be
OL,18,Ffelt across the wider economy.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
