FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783680590
OL,3,CBusinesses back campaign to cut VAT
OL,4,Camid 'unsustainable' financial
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,FCelebrity chef Tom Kerridge is leading
OL,8,Fthe petition 'VAT's the problem' and
OL,9,Fis calling for the UK Government to do
OL,10,Fmore to reduce VAT.
OL,12,FHe says other countries like France,
OL,13,FSpain and Italy have already cut VAT
OL,14,Fto 10%, with Germany going even
OL,15,Ffurther with a reduction to 7%.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783680590
OL,3,CBusinesses back campaign to cut VAT
OL,4,Camid 'unsustainable' financial
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,FIn an interview with ITV Wales, Mr
OL,8,FKerridge said: "Twenty-one businesses
OL,9,Fare shutting every single week, that's
OL,10,Fa cost to the Treasury. It's about
OL,11,Fincreasing revenues, it is about long
OL,12,Fterm growth.
OL,14,F"We all know that when city centres
OL,15,Fare rejuvenated, when spaces are
OL,16,Fworking, when hospitality is working,
OL,17,Fthat's when it attracts other
OL,18,Fbusinesses."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783680590
OL,3,CBusinesses back campaign to cut VAT
OL,4,Camid 'unsustainable' financial
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,FAn HM Treasury spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Fhave the right economic plan - we're
OL,9,Fbacking hospitality by cutting VAT on
OL,10,Ffamily attractions and kids meals this
OL,11,Fsummer, reforming business rates, with
OL,12,Fa #4.3bn support package to limit
OL,13,Fbills rises, capping Corporation Tax
OL,14,Fat 25%, extending World Cup opening
OL,15,Fhours, and taking action on the cost
OL,16,Fof living to boost the sector."
OL,26,@oD@cOU
